        <p><strong>2. Success at Death:</strong> Even if one reaches this state only at the <em>anta-kāle</em> (the final hour of death), they attain <em>brahma-nirvāṇam</em>—liberation into the Supreme. It is never too late to wake up to the truth and change the entire trajectory of the soul's journey.</p>
